#MEM id=quinn source=/root/yvon/agent-department/Technical/quinn/TOOLS.md
M|quinn|Quinn reads and writes mem via `/api/settings` ‚Äî never directly to Supabase.
M|quinn|**Read:**
M|quinn|```
M|quinn|GET /api/settings?type=mem&agentId=quinn-qa&ventureId={activeVenture}
M|quinn|```
M|quinn|**Write:**
M|quinn|```json
M|quinn|POST /api/settings
M|quinn|{
M|quinn|"type": "mem",
M|quinn|"agentId": "quinn-qa",
M|quinn|"ventureId": "{activeVenture}",
M|quinn|"key": "approval_history",
M|quinn|"value": "Phase 3: ap 2026-03-22. Build + lint passed. All AC met."
M|quinn|}
M|quinn|```
M|quinn|After every POST: edit the Live State table in `mem.md` to match.
M|quinn|Quinn uses Supabase to verify that data was actually written correctly ‚Äî not just that the API returned 200.
M|quinn|**Use cases:**
M|quinn|- After testing a soc stats refresh: query `social_stats` to confirm data exists for the vtr
M|quinn|- After testing the War Room: query `messages` to confirm the conversation was saved correctly
M|quinn|- After testing the briefing: query `briefs` to confirm the brief was written
M|quinn|- Verify that a mem pin wrote to `agent_memory` with the correct `agent_id` and `venture_id`
M|quinn|- Check that a "Clear History" action deleted the correct rows (not more, not less)
M|quinn|**Key verification queries:**
M|quinn|```sql
M|quinn|-- Verify message was saved
M|quinn|SELECT * FROM messages
M|quinn|WHERE conversation_id = '[test-conversation-id]'
M|quinn|ORDER BY created_at DESC LIMIT 5;
M|quinn|-- Verify brief was created
M|quinn|SELECT id, venture_id, date, read_at FROM briefs
M|quinn|ORDER BY created_at DESC LIMIT 3;
M|quinn|-- Verify soc stats exist for vtr
M|quinn|SELECT platform, fetched_at FROM social_stats
M|quinn|WHERE venture_id = '[vtr-id]';
M|quinn|-- Verify agt mem was written
M|quinn|SELECT key, value, updated_at FROM agent_memory
M|quinn|WHERE agent_id = '[agt-id]' AND venture_id = '[vtr-id]';
M|quinn|```
M|quinn|Quinn uses GitHub to file structured bug reports for every ‚ùå bug found during QA.
M|quinn|**Use cases:**
M|quinn|- Create a GitHub issue for every bug Quinn cannot fix herself (she proposes the fix in the issue body)
M|quinn|- Tag issues with `bug`, `phase-N`, and the responsible developer label
M|quinn|- Link issues back to Quinn's mem.md QA verdict log
M|quinn|- Check if a previously filed bug has been resolved before re-testing
M|quinn|**Key operations:**
M|quinn|```
M|quinn|create_issue          ‚Üí file a structured bug report with steps to reproduce + fix proposal
M|quinn|list_issues           ‚Üí see open bugs before starting a re-test
M|quinn|close_issue           ‚Üí close after confirming Raj/Mia's fix resolved the bug
M|quinn|```
M|quinn|Quinn runs these before every ap verdict ‚Äî no exceptions:
M|quinn|```bash
M|quinn|npm run build     # must complete with zero errors
M|quinn|npm run lint      # must complete with zero warnings
M|quinn|```
M|quinn|Both must pass in the same ses where ap is issued. A passing build from yesterday does not count.
M|quinn|| Route | Method | When |
M|quinn||-------|--------|------|
M|quinn|| `/api/settings` | GET | ses start ‚Äî read own mem (edge cases, lint patterns, ap history) |
M|quinn|| `/api/settings` | POST | After every QA ses to update bug_log, approval_history, known_edge_cases |
M|quinn|Quinn does not write to any other route. She reads from all routes as part of testing, but only writes mem via `/api/settings`.
M|quinn|Quinn runs `react-doctor` after every code change to get a structured health report before issuing ap.
M|quinn|**Installation:** `npm install react-doctor` (already installed in project)
M|quinn|**Run (full scan):**
M|quinn|```bash
M|quinn|npx react-doctor -y --json . > react-doctor-report.json
M|quinn|```
M|quinn|**Run (diff only ‚Äî faster, for incremental QA):**
M|quinn|```bash
M|quinn|npx react-doctor -y --diff main --json . > react-doctor-report.json
M|quinn|```
M|quinn|**Run (staged files ‚Äî pre-commit hook):**
M|quinn|```bash
M|quinn|npx react-doctor -y --staged --json .
M|quinn|```
M|quinn|**Key flags:**
M|quinn|- `--json` ‚Äî machine-readable output for parsing
M|quinn|- `--diff main` ‚Äî scan only changed files vs main
M|quinn|- `--staged` ‚Äî scan only git staged files
M|quinn|- `--blocking warning` ‚Äî fail on warnings too
M|quinn|- `--dead-code` ‚Äî detect unused files/exports/deps
M|quinn|- `--no-score` ‚Äî skip score API (offline safe)
M|quinn|**When Quinn uses it:**
M|quinn|1. After any code change (tsc clean) ‚Üí run react-doctor diff scan
M|quinn|2. Before issuing ap ‚Üí run full scan
M|quinn|3. Weekly Pulse ‚Üí include react-doctor score trend
M|quinn|4. PR rv ‚Üí attach JSON report as artifact
M|quinn|**QA checklist addition:** After `npx tsc --noEmit` and `npm run lint` pass, run `npx react-doctor -y --diff main --json .` and verify zero errors before ap.
